♫ is what we're proud of ♫

11
00:00:49,970 --> 00:00:53,999
♫ I'm walking toward you ♫

12
00:00:54,000 --> 00:00:56,919
♫ You suddenly break in ♫

13
00:00:56,920 --> 00:00:59,519
♫ and also open up my heart ♫

14
