597
00:35:25,159 --> 00:35:27,198
You'll benefit from it.

598
00:35:27,199 --> 00:35:29,198
I used to go up the mountain every day.

599
00:35:29,199 --> 00:35:32,760
I know every flower, tree and bush here.

600
